**Python Website Hosting on AWS EC2 Linux Instance. **
Hosting a Python web app on an AWS Linux instance is a great way to get hands-on with cloud infrastructure. Letâ€™s break it down into two parts: the **deployment steps** and a **simple architecture diagram** ğŸ§±ğŸ

